c: 8
v: 19
t: "Ngati inu mufunsa chiweruzo, tsopano chiweruzo chadza kwa inu ndipo ngati inu musiya kuchita zoipa zidzakhala bwino kwa inu ndipo ngati inu mubwerera, Ifenso tidzabwerera ndipo magulu anu a nkhondo, ngakhale kuti ndi ochuluka, sadzakuthandizani china chilichonse ndipo, ndithudi, Mulungu ali kumbali ya anthu okhulupirira"